-- SAIL to Sell 5% Stake, Government to Match, Seeks Bankers to Manage Sale
-- Natalie Obiko Pearson
-- 2010-08-02T01:32:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/sail-to-sell-5-stake-government-to-match-seeks-bankers-to-manage-sale.html

          
          
             The Steel Authority of India Ltd.
plans to sell a 5 percent stake and the government will sell an
equal share in a follow-on public offer, the company said in an
advertisement in the Economic Times today. Banks interested in
managing the sale have until Aug. 23, 5:30 p.m. local time to
submit bids, it said.  
